---
title: Mexican Tortilla Stacks with Guacamole and Black Bean Salsa
description: For this recipe, we took classic Mexican ingredients and played with the presentation to create something that’s as tasty to the eye as it is to the tongue. Consider it a savory version of a Napoleon!
